dc_title_s: South America, Venezuela, Golfo de Venezuela, Entrance to Bahía de Tablazo (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From Venezuelan and British Admiralty charts to 1986." "Copyright 1995 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram and tidal information. Map No. 24483. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA). United States. Defense Mapping Agency. (1995). South America, Venezuela, Golfo de Venezuela, Entrance to Bahía de Tablazo (Raster Image). LandInfo. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/bv675cp6075 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
